metadata.name: Cyber Station 3098
metadata.description:
In Super galaxy the Station number -"three 0 nine eight" is a hive of activity. There is something on the station that is almost like a city in its own right. Life on this particular station seemed to revolved around cybernetics, futuristic tech . The generation of people is developed and it's a revolution of future where human and Android Models live together peacefully.  
This city has all the source that need to live life.
